{
    "fields": {
        "project": {
            "key": "{{jiraKey}}"
        },
        "parent": {
            "key": "{{key}}"
        },
        "summary": "Assign All Sub-Tasks (in your Training) To You",

        "description": {
            "version": 1,
            "type": "doc",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": {
                        "level": 1
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Quick version:"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Assign all sub-task underneath the parent training to yourself."
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": {
                        "level": 1
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Summary:"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "The Assignee on a Jira issue (aka Ticket) is the person that has the next related action on the issue "
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "or",
                            "marks": [
                                {
                                    "type": "strike"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": " is the person who owns outcome and statusing "
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "or",
                            "marks": [
                                {
                                    "type": "strike"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": " someone that is going to triage the issue to assign to someone else.  In any case the \"Assignee\" is the owner of any issue - and there can only be one.  Being an Assignee on your work is a good thing because it allows you to track your work. Here, all the sub-tasks in your training ticket are unassigned. Let's assign them to all to you. There are two methods we will practice. Assigning ticket from parent and going into each issue for assignment. "
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": {
                        "level": 1
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Actions to Complete:"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "orderedList",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "listItem",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "paragraph",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Go to the parent ticket of this sub-task, so you can see all sub-tasks"
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "listItem",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "paragraph",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Go through the sub-tasks and assign them to you by using the (...) next to each sub-task"
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "listItem",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "paragraph",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "For the last two â€“ actually navigate into the subtask"
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "listItem",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "paragraph",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Then mark "
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "this",
                                            "marks": [
                                                {
