{
    "fields": {
        "project": {
            "key": "{{jiraKey}}"
        },
        "parent": {
            "key": "{{key}}"
        },
        "summary": "Edit A Confluence Page",

          "description": {
            "version": 1,
            "type": "doc",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": {
                        "level": 1
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Quick version:"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Go to \"AKS-24: Hello Confluence\" page and make a fun edit."
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": {
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "About Confluence "
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Confluence "
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "pages",
                            "marks": [
                                {
                                    "type": "em"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": " allow for sharing and editing a live document --similar to Wikipedia. Confluence has a lot of capability for  collaboration,  content curation, and sharing. "
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": {
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Some Philosophy"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "In areas where teams are working together it can be beneficial to take on an ethos \"if you are reading something and can make it better just do it\".  This is opposed to relaying to the author recommendations for changes.  In some circumstances this can be wasteful since the author is essentially tracking changes that a recommender has already typed out once. Also, this relaying of information can lead to waste through duplication of effort and misinterpretations.  Confluence has a rich revision history so you do not need to be worried about ruining someone's sauce."
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Note: an exception to this ethos would be controlled documents where changes need to review and approved. "
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": {
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "What We Will Do"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "We will practice with a very trivial example. We'll go to a \"Hello Confluence\" page and update it to let everyone know we made it."
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": {
                        "level": 1
                    },
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Actions to Complete:"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "orderedList",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "listItem",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "paragraph",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Navigate to the Confluence page: "
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "AKS-24: Hello Confluence",
                                            "marks": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "link",
                                                    "attrs": {
                                                        "href": "https://upstartnetwork.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/AKS/pages/391578555/AKS-24+Hello+Confluence"
                                                    }
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "listItem",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "paragraph",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "You will default into \"viewing\" mode, but we want to edit.  Navigate to the pencil icon in top right of the page. Click it to enter into edit mode"
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "listItem",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "paragraph",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Made an edit to let people know you made it.  Feel free to add text, pictures, emojis."
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "listItem",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "paragraph",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Click Publish to push this page"
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "listItem",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "paragraph",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Take a screenshot of the new page and attach it to this issue."
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "listItem",
                            "content": [
                                {
                                    "type": "paragraph",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Mark this issue as done"
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },



        "issuetype": {
            "name": "Sub-task"
        }
    }
}

