                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "As you get more comfortable with the Atlasssian tools it will make sense to include Jira references into Confluence pages. Sometimes it will make sense to reference these links in the page titles, sometimes you just want to add the live Jira link into the Confluence body.  We will start by adding the link into the Confluence page body of a personalized training report that has already been created for you. At this point we are simply practicing the mechanics of the Jira links. "
