                                                }
                                            ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": " and use the left hand navigation to find your training report under the Training Report section.  Note, that your training page with be prefixed with the same key as the main/parent issue of your training Jira ticket (take note of this issue number)"
